msgid ""
"Custom splash screen for this reader. Leave blank to auto-generate from your "
"site logo. Splash screens are uploaded to Stripe when the reader is "
"registered."
msgstr ""
"Layar awal khusus untuk pembaca ini. Biarkan kosong untuk menghasilkan "
"otomatis dari logo situs Anda. Layar awal diunggah ke Stripe saat pembaca "
"terdaftar."

